
Overview of noun hysteria

The noun hysteria has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                       
1. (1) craze, delirium, frenzy, fury, hysteria -- (state of violent mental agitation)
2. (1) hysteria -- (excessive or uncontrollable fear)
3. hysteria, hysterical neurosis -- (neurotic disorder characterized by violent emotional outbreaks and disturbances of sensory and motor functions)
